data.description: Situated in the highly coveted Dix River Estates, this luxurious home sits right in front of hole 14 of the 18 hole Dix River Country Club golf course. Your backyard is a golfer's dream with a meticulously maintained 18-hole golf course right at your doorstep. Enjoy tee times at your leisure and savor the breathtaking views of rolling fairways. Unwind in your private sauna after a long day. Whether you're seeking relaxation or relief from stress, this space will rejuvenate your body and mind. As you walk into the home, you will immediately notice the spacious sunroom. Bask in the warmth of the sun as you sip your morning coffee or read a book or choose to relax by your gas fireplace in the family room. The kitchen features maple cabinetry with an electric cooktop, pullout spice rack, built in wall oven and soft close cabinets. The home boasts 4 generous bedrooms and 3 bathrooms and walk-in closets with an additional room and half bath over the garage with private staircase. With beautiful, oak, custom built-ins in the formal living/office you will recognize all of the detail that went into this meticulously well-built home. This home will be sold as-is. Inspections welcome.
